Color Inversion: Ensure game_env.py uses the BGRX to RGB conversion, otherwise the AI will be "colorblind."

    Window Focus: The SuperTux window must be the active window for virtual inputs to register.

    Aspect Ratio: Running the game at 1280x720 (16:9) provides the best results for the Vision Transformer model.


